  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA92">
<l>makaṉoruvark kallāta māmēṉi māyaṉ</l>
<l>makaṉā mavaṉmakaṉṟaṉ kātaṉ – makaṉaic</l>
<l>ciṟaiceyta vāṇaṉṟōḷ ceṟṟāṉ kaḻalē</l>
<l>niṟaiceyteṉ ṉeñcē niṉai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The trickster with a dark body who is not the son of anyone</l>
<l>became a son. The one who subdued the arms of Bāṇa<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">The grandson of Kṛṣṇa is Aniruddha, son of Kṛṣṇa’s son Pradyumna; cf. Pē. 80.1f. note.</note>, who put into prison</l>
<l>the beloved son of the son of him, make yourself full</l>
<l>of the ankleted [feet of him], my heart, think!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
